==================================

This file records third-party material used by tekken-coach and the licensing posture for
each. The governing principle (docs/05 §3.1, docs/02 §5) is a strict **data-vs-code split**:
we ingest community *data* with attribution, and we never vendor restrictively-licensed
application *code*.


1. Frame data — tekkendocs.com / rbnorway.org (DATA, used with attribution)
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Source repository : https://github.com/pbruvoll/tekkendocs
Ingested files    : data/wavuConvertedCsv/<char>/*.csv  (Wavu-derived, CSV-normalized)
Attribution       : tekkendocs.com, rbnorway.org
Used in           : assets/framedata/  (snapshots; see each manifest.json for the pinned SHA)

Posture:
  - The frame *data* is community-sourced and used here WITH ATTRIBUTION.
  - The `pbruvoll/tekkendocs` application *code* is RESTRICTIVELY LICENSED and is NOT copied,
    vendored, adapted, or redistributed in this project. Only the published data is ingested.
